  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3288600/extras/b964deec53b8f3acde2cd00df6d04146.poster.avif?t=1758563303\" width=600 height=178 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3288600/extras/b964deec53b8f3acde2cd00df6d04146.webm?t=1758563303\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3288600/extras/b964deec53b8f3acde2cd00df6d04146.mp4?t=1758563303\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>Skibidi Gyatrooms</strong> is a 1-4 player<strong> co-op horror</strong> exploration game. You and the homies just fell into the Backrooms, but these ain’t no ordinary halls. The only thing scarier than being stuck in liminal spaces is the Skibidi Toilet coming at you with max rizz and zero chill.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3288600/extras/e9595d144b496df24ab962441824977a.poster.avif?t=1758563303\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3288600/extras/e9595d144b496df24ab962441824977a.webm?t=1758563303\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3288600/extras/e9595d144b496df24ab962441824977a.mp4?t=1758563303\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > You gotta out-GYAT that porcelain sigma menace before it flushes you with no remorse. Think you got the sauce to escape solo? Bet, but don’t sleep on bringing the squad. We’re talking wild updates, cursed levels, and enough brainrot to make your head spin. Will you survive the GYAT or get flushed?<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3288600/extras/53b73ee189855e892afc28d4a8a411db.poster.avif?t=1758563303\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3288600/extras/53b73ee189855e892afc28d4a8a411db.webm?t=1758563303\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3288600/extras/53b73ee189855e892afc28d4a8a411db.mp4?t=1758563303\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
